{"tid":1381464,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］一人一枝梳打水好嗎？","createTime":"2019-07-29T08:48:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T14:07:23.000Z","uid":167634,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d9aedc6467e8c8281d91edd9e4c541184879a19d","tid":1381464,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:48:39.000Z","msg":"Baking Soda＋水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URQbCbZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURQbCbZ.png&h=8ec55819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SQGFvw0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSQGFvw0.png&h=370b3919&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&quot;Because tear gas is not actually a gas but a very fine acid powder, its effectiveness can be easily mitigated by any over the counter anti acid drug commonly available at drugstores or pharmacy without prescription, like sodium bicarbonate (baking soda), Maalox or Alka-Seltzer to name a few.&quot; <br />\n<br />\nTEAR GAS ANTIDOTE RECIPES <br />\n<br />\nNeutralizer #1 - Spray or squirt bottle of water with 1-2 Tablespoons of Baking Soda. <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.indybay.org/newsitems/2011/10/26/18695225.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indybay.org%2Fnewsitems%2F2011%2F10%2F26%2F18695225.php&d=SfvWO4iieP9%2B5ivoSMB2BgX2xtV6HnGzrHUHOMeG36I%3D&h=8f69a34f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.indybay.org/newsitems/2011/10/26/18695225.php</a>"},{"pid":"5061b8703a1cc80ede525a709ff622d07a1d6ea4","tid":1381464,"uid":91771,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d9aedc6467e8c8281d91edd9e4c541184879a19d","tid":1381464,"uid":167634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T08:48:39.000Z","msg":"Baking Soda＋水<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URQbCbZ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURQbCbZ.png&h=8ec55819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.c